== Papia Tum re nirbhagia ==




Papia tum re nirbhagia,

tum pap nam sanddxi  !

sasnnachea sasnnak, papia, 

iemkonddant pavxi  !




Dhon  ani grestkai,  papia,

hangach dovorxi;

tujeo kornnio gheun, papia,

zhott’ttak re vexi.



Hanga pap tuj’ dhampolam,

thoi tem ugtem zait.

Devagelo xrap, papia,

tujer re poddot.



Soitan nhoi re, papia,

dusman re tuzo;

iemkonddant zaxi, papia

gulam re tazo.



Devan rochila, papia,

sorgachea sukhak;

kiteak tum vetai, papia,

sasnnachea dukhak ?



Pap bhogsuncheak re, papia, 

upai re sompo:

ontoskomna-dukh, papia,

an’nichev khoro.



Kumsarak vochunk, papia, 

loz dhori naka:

Somi [[Jezu|Jezu Krist]], papia,

ravta re tuka



Devacho re Put, papia,

monisu zalo

sorgar thaun tuka, papia,

soddounk re ailo

